      <title>乌克兰议会推进允许双重国籍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ukraine-s-parliament-moves-forward-on-allowing-dual-citizenship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰将放宽双重国籍禁令，以应对俄罗斯全面入侵引发的人口危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ukraine-s-parliament-moves-forward-on-allowing-dual-citizenship</guid>
